            <note xml:id="foot.f2">No reply to this letter has been found, but a note added to the cited passage in the second edition of <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_2400.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Expression</hi></ref> remarked that bitches often vomited up food for their young when the young had reached a certain age (<ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_2401.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Expression</hi> 2d ed.</ref>, p. 271 n. 11).</note>
